### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### User Registration
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### User Login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get User Profile (replace TOKEN with actual token)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Search Movies
GET http://localhost:3001/api/movies/search?query=inception&page=1

### Get Popular Movies
GET http://localhost:3001/api/movies/popular?page=1

### Get Top Rated Movies
GET http://localhost:3001/api/movies/top-rated?page=1

### Get Movie Genres
GET http://localhost:3001/api/movies/genres

### Get Movie Details (replace MOVIE_ID with actual TMDB movie ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/movies/550

### Create Review (replace TOKEN and MOVIE_ID)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/reviews/550
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 9,
  "text": "Amazing movie! One of my favorites."
}

### Get User Reviews (replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/reviews/user
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Add to Watchlist (replace TOKEN and MOVIE_ID)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/watchlist/550
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Get User Watchlist (replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Check Watchlist Status (replace TOKEN and MOVIE_ID)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/watchlist/550/status
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
